{"tid":367757,"cid":7,"subCid":0,"title":"唔理靚靚反對　Chilam培育魔童做電競高手","createTime":"2017-08-21T04:00:44.000Z","updateTime":"2017-08-21T09:46:40.000Z","uid":22675,"like":3,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"fcdeb5d36e2ae3f6f474f691a201ac6bb4fc7dc6","tid":367757,"uid":22675,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-21T04:00:44.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=us0Edvp6Uqg\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3Dus0Edvp6Uqg&d=gaqVBlAyGboJEH5G65GD%2BIS5T71%2BpEKm9yZKOKwCwR4%3D&h=0129151f\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=us0Edvp6Uqg</a><br />\n發佈日期：2017年8月20日<br />\n袁詠儀出席活動，好多時話題都離唔開囝囝張慕童。最近佢就大爆魔童想做打機達人，不過靚靚呢個嚴媽梗係唔俾啦，講到明讀書第一呀！好彩老豆Chilam最知阿仔心意，趁住放暑假，即刻撇低老婆，帶埋囝囝同佢個表兄弟去灣仔電腦廣場揀電子遊戲。<br />\n<br />\n一行三人首先買返個充電火牛先，斷估係屋企原裝嗰個壞咗啦。之後入到game舖，Chilam成個細路咁，揀得仲認真過兩個小朋友。問題嚟喇，無遮無掩嘅Chilam四圍行，竟然無人集佢郵，相當少見。<br />\n<br />\n巡完一間又一間，Chilam兩父子踎晒地搭晒膊頭不停研究，感情好好，friend過打band！買完game之後直踩去便利店歎思樂冰消消暑。<br />\n<br />\n直到臨開車走人，終於有fans上前要求合照喇，平時嘅Chilam永無托手踭，不過今次佢笑笑口咁say no，無非都係唔想魔童等啫，因為個仔趕住返屋企做打機達人呀！只能夠話呢個廿四孝型爸無得輸。"},{"pid":"34d4027e28b6e0f1f9d1093bc7a410ea5695a4b7","tid":367757,"uid":22675,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-21T04:39:06.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e41161bd297a2048dd4511ebc15b78b6e9fbbce7","tid":367757,"uid":22675,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-21T06:50:49.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0fba22dc4393e53d954075be87e49207102d09aa","tid":367757,"uid":51720,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-21T09:45:45.000Z","msg":"原來「雲外看，新生趣」係咁解 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"13ce44f98051985fcadc10da9a0a932f2d501f8e","tid":367757,"uid":62409,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"